I am Carl Marco E. Ungos.
I was born in Pasig City on July 21,1999
My parents are Eladia Ungos and Alberto Ungos III and I'm their only son.
We used to live in Taytay, Rizal but after 4 years of living there, we transferred to Mandaluyong.
I studied in St. Therese Educational Private School during my elementary years.
I then went to the City of Mandaluyong Science High School to continue my studies and I stayed there for 6 years.
During the summer between senior high and college, I worked at Mcdonald's for about 3 months.
Today, I am a 2nd Year student of the Royal and Pontifical School of the Philippines, the University of Santo Tomas currently taking up Bachelor of Science Major in Electronics Engineering.
